41:44.169 --> 41:46.738
CONRAD:
You broke into Julian's place?

41:46.772 --> 41:48.406
DEVON:
Not exactly.

41:48.439 --> 41:50.909
The landlady let me in
to get Julian's cat.

41:50.942 --> 41:52.644
Don't ask.

41:52.678 --> 41:55.747
-And you just took
her phone bill.
-Yes.

41:55.781 --> 41:58.049
Look at the last number
that Julian called.

41:58.083 --> 42:01.186
On the 3rd,
the day I saw her in the park.

42:01.219 --> 42:02.754
The day she disappeared.

42:02.788 --> 42:04.723
I tried the number
about an hour ago

42:04.756 --> 42:07.325
and I got an answering machine.

42:07.358 --> 42:10.495
It was an office at the FDA.

42:10.528 --> 42:12.363
Julian was a device rep.

42:12.397 --> 42:13.932
She probably called them
all the time.

42:13.965 --> 42:15.233
Or maybe she found something out

42:15.266 --> 42:17.402
and she was trying
to blow the whistle.

42:19.237 --> 42:22.741
Look, you said it yourself.

42:22.774 --> 42:25.777
Bradley died because
of a defective valve.

42:27.045 --> 42:29.715
He was my best friend.

42:29.748 --> 42:33.118
Did QuoVadis know
the valve was bad?

42:33.151 --> 42:37.422
If so, they killed him.

42:37.455 --> 42:40.191
Julian told me that something
was wrong at work.

42:40.225 --> 42:44.029
She felt like
everything was falling apart.

42:44.062 --> 42:45.897
What do you think she meant?

42:47.232 --> 42:49.735
I think she was in danger.

42:49.768 --> 42:53.238
Did they kill her?
Did she run away?

42:53.271 --> 42:55.941
I don't know.

42:55.974 --> 42:58.910
Something is up with QuoVadis.

43:03.248 --> 43:04.449
(Nic sighs)

